    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. A planned re-validation against updated boundary-condition measurements following the February 2026 model revision is scheduled for Q2 2026 to close the open item on the Model Inputs factor.",
